data.description: Motivated Seller! Stunning single level 3,251 SqFt home on 4.5 acres showcasing 4 Bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms Home with amazing views of the San Gabriel Mountains! Walk inside and you’re greeted by large open ceilings and floor plan; a large dining area and living room! Open floor plan between the kitchen and family room with access to the enclosed back porch! The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, double ovens and plenty of cabinet space! The bedrooms are spacious and the primary bedroom has a dream custom closet with plenty of storage space! The large primary bedroom showcases a sitting area, which is the perfect spot to read a book next to the fireplace! In additions to the primary are 2 bedroom suites that each have their own full bathroom. Additional features include a Large attached 3 car garage and an ADDITIONAL detached workshop/garage, gym and storage space! The perfect spot for all your hobbies and toys! Gym equipment to remain. This home also features a wine cellar detached from the home! Large back patio and enclosed back porch! Entertainer delight! This property has a large circle drive way, fenced lot and plenty of space for gardening! In additional to all the space is a fenced chicken coop! This property has all that you’ve been looking for! Solar panels recently added to the home! Enjoy all the beauty and potential that this home has to offer - schedule your showing today!
